del pas, triplicar la participacin del segundo competidor, premios a la efectividad (Effies)y miles de mams que habla as de la marca:\n\nganar 10 (Effies) entre otras.\n\nAl final, todos estos logros comprobaron que cuando se tiene un arma tan poderosa como lo es entender el amor de una mam, es posible ganar todas las batallas.'),(3866,1545,'_segundo_parrafo_article','field_5a42ba8223eff'),(3867,1545,'video_de_contenido','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eEuw6Xlq_zM'),(3868,1545,'_video_de_contenido','field_5a42bb2923f01'),(3869,1545,'tercer_parrafo_article',''),(3870,1545,'_tercer_parrafo_article','field_5a42ba9e23f00'),(3871,1545,'check_external_link','0'),(3872,1545,'_check_external_link','field_5a2efcec98b98'),(3873,1545,'destacado','0'),(3874,1545,'_destacado','field_5a3bc38cbc94d'),(3875,1545,'textos_grilla','1'),(3876,1545,'_textos_grilla','field_5a57c224d3cb5'),(3877,1545,'_wpml_media_duplicate','1'),(3878,1545,'_wpml_media_featured','1'),(3879,1545,'external_link','http://localhost/sanchobbdo/sancho-bbdo-colombia/el-amor-nuestra-mejor-apuesta/'),(3880,1545,'_external_link','field_5a2efd3698b99'),(3881,1547,'_thumbnail_id','1461'),(3882,1547,'eg_sources_html5_mp4',''),(3883,1547,'eg_sources_html5_ogv',''),(3884,1547,'eg_sources_html5_webm',''),(3885,1547,'eg_sources_youtube',''),(3886,1547,'eg_sources_vimeo',''),(3887,1547,'eg_sources_wistia',''),(3888,1547,'eg_sources_image',''),(3889,1547,'eg_sources_iframe',''),(3890,1547,'eg_sources_soundcloud',''),(3891,1547,'eg_vimeo_ratio','0'),(3892,1547,'eg_youtube_ratio','0'),(3893,1547,'eg_wistia_ratio','0'),(3894,1547,'eg_html5_ratio','0'),(3895,1547,'eg_soundcloud_ratio','0'),(3896,1547,'eg_settings_custom_meta_skin',''),(3897,1547,'eg_settings_custom_meta_element',''),(3898,1547,'eg_settings_custom_meta_setting',''),(3899,1547,'eg_settings_custom_meta_style',''),(3900,1547,'eg_custom_meta_216','true'),(3901,1547,'eg-origen','SANCHO BBDO '),(3902,1547,'type','image'),(3903,1547,'_type','field_5a4e5b3322ffc'),(390